### âœ” When should you use POST?

ğŸ‘‰ **When creating connector first time**

### âœ” When should you use PUT?

ğŸ‘‰ **When updating an existing connector**

ğŸ’¡ If you run POST again for same connector name â†’ you will get:

```
Connector already exists
```

Then you must use:

```
